<title>USA: HealthRite appoints CEO and CFO.</title>
<headline>HealthRite appoints CEO and CFO.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>HealthRite Inc said Thursday that President and Chief Operating Officer Bradley MacDonald had been appointed chief executive officer, and Executive Vice President Robert Pugaczewski had been named chief financial officer.</p>
<p>HealthRite also said it had completed an equity financing of $865,000 to fund a launch of health and fitness products.</p>
